00:24:32,588 --> 00:24:37,857
Tucker. She's in surgery.

440
00:24:37,960 --> 00:24:41,111
She's literally saving a life
and she's gonna be here soon.

441
00:24:41,214 --> 00:24:42,958
She's always
saving a person's life.

442
00:24:42,982 --> 00:24:45,049
She'll always be here soon.

443
00:24:45,134 --> 00:24:48,969
You go ask her, when
exactly is soon gonna come?

444
00:25:01,067 --> 00:25:05,535
Excuse me. You're... You're
the one who came to get me.

445
00:25:05,637 --> 00:25:09,423
- Who told me about Stan.
- Yes.

446
00:25:09,525 --> 00:25:12,693
- Is Ray...?
- He's in surgery.

447
00:25:13,996 --> 00:25:16,463
OK. I have to go.

448
00:25:16,565 --> 00:25:19,399
I have to get out of here, so...

449
00:25:21,037 --> 00:25:24,988
Look, can you tell
him that I'm sorry?

450
00:25:25,091 --> 00:25:27,975
I can't stay here? I just can't
come back here right now?

451
00:25:28,093 --> 00:25:31,644
Ray wanted me to tell
you that he's sorry too.

452
00:25:31,746 --> 00:25:33,992
He's sorry he
couldn't save Stan.

453
00:25:34,016 --> 00:25:37,234
He wanted me to tell you
that in case he didn't make it.

454
00:25:40,072 --> 00:25:43,873
- Think he's not gonna make it?
- I hope he makes it.

455
00:25:43,975 --> 00:25:45,942
But you won't be here, so...

456
00:25:48,614 --> 00:25:50,614
My husband is dead.

457
00:25:51,683 --> 00:25:55,819
He's dead. Somewhere
in this hospital.

458
00:25:56,789 --> 00:25:59,289
How am I supposed to stay here?

459
00:25:59,391 --> 00:26:01,891
<i>♪ Her heart in her throat ♪</i>

460
00:26:01,993 --> 00:26:04,127
I don't know.

461
00:26:04,229 --> 00:26:06,380
I don't know.

462
00:26:06,482 --> 00:26:08,960
But I know that if Ray makes it,

463
00:26:08,984 --> 00:26:12,352
he's gonna wake up and
he's gonna have no one.

464
00:26:12,454 --> 00:26:16,222
And you're gonna go home
and you're gonna have...

465
00:26:16,324 --> 00:26:17,557
No one.

466
00:26:17,659 --> 00:26:22,045
I think it's better to have
